    "name": "Serafina's Saga: Awakened",
    "steam_appid": 2369430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369430/extras/092d6daa2dea77b4ff7bf781660a4b9e.avif?t=1713216823\" width=611 height=71 /></span><br>Young Serafina has spent her entire life alone in the jungle with only her guardian, a mysterious man named Arken, as company. When Arken is captured by a group of soldiers and carried away, Serafina must venture outside the forest to save him. On her journey to the heart of the kingdom, Serafina discovers a whole new world beyond the shadows of the jungle.<br><br>From the depths of the jungle to the bustling Castle of Krondolee, you must decide for yourself who to trust. Your decision will help Serafina uncover the truth of her past, rescue Arken, and possibly save the kingdom.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369430/extras/6a033eed0dc1d54bc3812aaa0dd25f0c.avif?t=1713216823\" width=611 height=71 /></span><br>Start by befriending your possible companions, then choose a partner for romance and a unique story branch. Perhaps you'll choose the strong and stoic Jezu, playful Nikolaos, chaotic Valerie, or the scheming and salacious Reuben.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369430/extras/688fe57f0fadfec64917ed9abd7e66f5.avif?t=1713216823\" width=610 height=158 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A complete remake of the original &quot;Serafina's Saga&quot; adventure<br></li><li>Choose between four distinct romances and story paths<br></li><li>Listen to a rich cast of English voice actors in select scenes<br></li><li>Enjoy a lush 3D environment developed in UE4<br></li><li>Hear a lengthy, dynamic soundtrack remixed and expanded from original game</li></ul>",
